OL,3,CNSPCC calls for 'law change' to
OL,4,Cprotect children from all physical
OL,5,Cpunishment
OL,7,FThe NSPCC has called for a law change
OL,8,Fto ensure children in Northern Ireland
OL,9,Fare protected from all physical
OL,10,Fpunishment.
OL,12,FCurrently the defence of "reasonable
OL,13,Fchastisement" allows parents and
OL,14,Fcarers to argue in court that it was
OL,15,Freasonable to use force against their
OL,16,Fchild.
OL,18,FIt comes as almost 70 countries around
OL,19,Fthe world, including Wales, Scotland
OL,20,Fand the Republic of Ireland, have put
OL,21,Fmeasures in place to protect children.
