OL,5,Cpunishment
OL,7,FThe NSPCC said the current defence of
OL,8,F"reasonable chastisement" means
OL,9,Fchildren in Northern Ireland are not
OL,10,Ffully protected from physical
OL,11,Fpunishment.
OL,13,FThe charity will lobby MLAs at an
OL,14,Fevent a Stormont today on the issue.
OL,16,FIt is proposing this change is made
OL,17,Fthrough the Justice Bill currently
OL,18,Fpassing through the Assembly.
