OL,5,Cpunishment
OL,7,FThe survey of over 1,000 members of
OL,8,Fthe public also found that only 14% of
OL,9,Fadults and 8% of parents considered
OL,10,Fphysical punishment an acceptable form
OL,11,Fof discipline.
OL,13,FThe charity is also calling for any
OL,14,Fchange in the law to be accompanied by
OL,15,Fimproved support for parents and
OL,16,Fcarers so they can manage their
OL,17,Fchildren's behaviour more effectively.
