OL,7,FCaroline Cunningham, policy and public
OL,8,Faffairs manager for NSPCC Northern
OL,9,FIreland, described a "crucial juncture
OL,10,Fin keeping children safer across
OL,11,FNorthern Ireland".
OL,13,F"We are grateful to everyone across
OL,14,Fthe statutory, community and political
OL,15,Fsectors who are attending to listen to
OL,16,Four goal to end physical punishment of
OL,17,Fchildren and young people," she said.
OL,19,F"We will hear today about the positive
OL,20,Fexperience since legal change in Wales.
