OL,7,F"We also need effective and improved
OL,8,Fsupport for parents and carers to
OL,9,Fmanage their children's behaviour more
OL,10,Fpositively.
OL,12,F"We urge our political parties in
OL,13,FNorthern Ireland to unite in giving
OL,14,Fchildren the protection they deserve.
OL,16,F"There is a clear message from the
OL,17,Fpublic with a majority view that
OL,18,Fphysical punishment should not be part
OL,19,Fof anyone's childhood.
