OL,3,CNSPCC calls for 'law change' to
OL,4,Cprotect children from all physical
OL,5,Cpunishment
OL,7,F"It is time to change the law to allow
OL,8,Fchildren in Northern Ireland a
OL,9,Fchildhood free of physical harm in any
OL,10,Fform."
OL,12,FConsultant paediatrician Dr Julie-Ann
OL,13,FManey added that it is known that
OL,14,Fphysical punishment has negative
OL,15,Fconsequences for children's physical
OL,16,Fand mental health and wellbeing as
OL,17,Fwell as their social, emotional and
OL,18,Fbehavioural outcomes.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@FO]
