OL,4,Cprotect children from all physical
OL,5,Cpunishment
OL,7,F"The lack of clarity around the
OL,8,Fcurrent laws in Northern Ireland makes
OL,9,Fit extremely challenging for
OL,10,Fpaediatricians to talk to families
OL,11,Fabout physical punishment," she said.
OL,13,F"This ambiguity not only undermines
OL,14,Fconversations about children's rights,
OL,15,Fwellbeing and safety, but also hinders
OL,16,Fclinicians from confidently advocating
OL,17,Ffor the best interests of the child.
