OL,3,CNSPCC calls for 'law change' to
OL,4,Cprotect children from all physical
OL,5,Cpunishment
OL,7,F"We need to give children here legal
OL,8,Fprotection from assault, and all its
OL,9,Fassociated harms.
OL,11,F"They deserve this as much as the
OL,12,Fchildren in the 68 other countries,
OL,13,Fincluding Scotland, Wales and the
OL,14,FRepublic of Ireland who have already
OL,15,Fimplemented this vital legislation."
OL,17,FThe NSPCC is urging members of the
OL,18,Fpublic to support equal protection for
OL,19,Fevery childhood through a change in
OL,20,Fthe law by signing the petition via
OL,21,Fits website.
